{"tid":2054350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本拒以聯合聲明批評黨安法 酒店業成走資落腳地或是誘因","createTime":"2020-06-07T06:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T06:23:28.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db73bbf44dbff090edd7bfe42b9b39bf43316dc8","tid":2054350,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"加山傳播 DB Channel<br />\n<br />\n【中國資金大規模走資 日本酒店業成落腳地】<br />\n<br />\n( 節錄 )<br />\n日本酒店業有被中資大規模進駐跡象。因武漢肺炎疫情，日本酒店入住率大減，許多選擇放售止蝕，因而引來大批中國富豪的興趣。更有指這些資金轉移，是為免中國強推「香港國安法」後，可能會遇上的制裁後遺。 <br />\n<br />\n文/N<br />\n#DBC #DBChannel #加山傳播 #武漢肺炎 #日本 #香港國安法 #光復香港時代革命<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=255063632576710&amp;set=a.122771689139239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%3Ffbid%3D255063632576710%26set%3Da.122771689139239&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=cce08a82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=255063632576710&amp;set=a.122771689139239</a><br />\n<br />\n共同社：日本拒以聯合聲明批評訂立港區國安法<br />\n07.06.2020 13:30<br />\n<br />\n共同社引述消息人士報道，日本政府拒絕應要求，參與英美等國的行列，以聯合聲明批評中國訂立港區國安法，表示日方是希望與中國改善關係，但美國等國家對日本做法感到失望。報道說，受疫情影響，國家主席習近平暫緩以國賓身份訪日，日方希望習近平最終能夠訪日，因此避免過度刺激中國。<br />\n<br />\n日本內閣官房長官菅義偉早前表示，對訂立港區國安法深表憂慮，其後外交部發言人趙立堅指出，為實現習近平作為國賓訪日，希望日方為此創造良好的環境和氛圍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1302252&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1302252%26csid%3D261_341&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=63fad443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1302252&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"900a1293cd94adc1e04088f64efe5753dd0f6b59","tid":2054350,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"德國日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e602ddf274dd0a84b990b341ba22687fc83552","tid":2054350,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900a1293cd94adc1e04088f64efe5753dd0f6b59","tid":2054350,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"德國日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"+ 法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c175e5abd44186d02c24b229a4d8499fffcd81","tid":2054350,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900a1293cd94adc1e04088f64efe5753dd0f6b59","tid":2054350,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"德國日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:22:44.000Z","msg":"熟悉的味道"},{"pid":"719c9552251eff77651948118950c1af8bfe2e91","tid":2054350,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900a1293cd94adc1e04088f64efe5753dd0f6b59","tid":2054350,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"德國日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"日本點會唔跟美國"}]}